00:37:27.840 --> 00:37:30.840
ang kalungkutan, sakit, at pananabik—

00:37:31.610 --> 00:37:33.570
lahat ng ito ay personal na emosyon.

00:37:34.700 --> 00:37:36.560
Nakabaon sila sa kaloob-looban dito.

00:37:36.880 --> 00:37:38.740
Ayokong hawakan sila ng iba.

00:37:40.230 --> 00:37:41.560
Hindi nila maintindihan.

00:37:41.630 --> 00:37:42.440
Oo.

